RT-Extension-FollowUp - Allow RT users to quickly add themself as Cc/AdminCc in the ticket action menu

This RT Extension adds two actions to the ticket actions
menu to allow the connected user with enough rights to add
himself as a Cc or AdminCc for this ticket.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Then, to make it active, add it to @Plugins in RT site configuration file
(RT_SiteConfig.pm), example:

    Set(@Plugins,qw(RT::Extension::FollowUp) );

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

You can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc RT::Extension::FollowUp


